<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>12664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔治讨厌蚯蚓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15092</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不喜欢触碰它们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19088</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他甚至不喜欢看到它们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19089</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呀！有只蚯蚓。我讨厌蚯蚓。”乔治尖叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35273</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？你讨厌我？你也讨厌那些美丽的花儿吗？”蚯蚓问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我喜欢它们。”乔治说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，那么，你也必须喜欢我。我帮助它们生长。”蚯蚓说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54439</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔治从没见过会说话的蚯蚓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54440</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，他还是不喜欢蚯蚓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68142</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是个大挖掘机。我挖洞有助于空气和水进入地里。”蚯蚓说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68143</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“植物生长需要大量的空气和水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有我，植物没法生长。”蚯蚓自豪地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85272</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，乔治还是不喜欢蚯蚓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85273</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我还为植物们做饭。”蚯蚓说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94815</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真的吗？怎么做？”乔治问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94816</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101201</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我吃下由植物碎屑和细菌混合而成的土粒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108212</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们进入我的身体再从另一端排出。”蚯蚓说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“植物们吃你的大便？”乔治笑着问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“说对了！这被称为肥料。”蚯蚓说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是你这么小。一只小蚯蚓能帮多大忙？”乔治问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126757</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔治不知道蚯蚓不只一只。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138094</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>甚至在乔治的小花园里，就有超过五百只蚯蚓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138095</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我所有的朋友一起帮助你的花园。”蚯蚓说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145298</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149008</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以你还讨厌我吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149009</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔治害羞地说：“不，但是你很脏，很恶心。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不脏。我很干净。摸摸我！”蚯蚓说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169364</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯……”乔治小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169365</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“来啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174949</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔治小心翼翼地摸了下蚯蚓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174950</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看！我没有那么糟。”蚯蚓说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180007</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你确实很软。”乔治承认说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189622</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在乔治开始喜欢蚯蚓了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189623</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196080</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，蚯蚓，你没有骨头。”乔治说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196081</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！我没有胳膊和腿。我不需要那些。”蚯蚓解释道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不需要那些？你怎么移动？”乔治问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我全身都是肌肉。我用它们在地上前行。看！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你去任何地方一定都需要很长时间。”乔治笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234348</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。我是一个缓慢的移动者，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234349</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是我很喜欢你的花园。所以我不想走远。”蚯蚓说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243049</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249143</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，我很高兴你在我的花园里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249144</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你是个很棒的帮手。”乔治微笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“记住，蚯蚓是你的朋友。”蚯蚓说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263994</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会的！”乔治说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>